'''布佐瓦'''（{{lang-uk|Бузова}}）是[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的村落，位於該國中北部[[基輔州|基輔州]]，由[[基輔-斯維亞托申區|基輔-斯維亞托申區]]負責管轄，始建於1648年，面積2.24平方公里，海拔高度164米，2001年人口1,548，人口密度每平方公里691.7人。

在[[2022年俄罗斯入侵乌克兰|2022年俄罗斯入侵乌克兰]]期间，俄罗斯军队袭击了當地的体育场，并在村外的飞机跑道上與烏克蘭軍隊作戰<ref>{{cite news |title='It was mayhem': A Belgian's escape from Ukraine |first=Dylan |last=Carter |date=11 March 2022 |url=https://www.brusselstimes.com/eu-affairs/210129/it-was-mayhem-a-belgians-escape-from-ukraine |newspaper=[[The_Brussels_Times|The Brussels Times]] |access-date=22 March 2022 |archive-date=2022-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313055424/https://www.brusselstimes.com/eu-affairs/210129/it-was-mayhem-a-belgians-escape-from-ukraine }}</ref>。2022年3月1日，俄軍炮击了高速公路旁的一個私立婦產科医院。<ref>{{cite news |title=A maternity hospital near Kyiv has been hit by a shell |date=1 March 2022 |url=https://www.pravda.com.ua/eng/news/2022/03/1/7327023/ |newspaper=[[Ukrayinska_Pravda|Ukrayinska Pravda]] |access-date=23 March 2022 |archive-date=2022-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323032120/https://www.pravda.com.ua/eng/news/2022/03/1/7327023/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Air raid alerts in Kyiv, Kharkiv and other cities: Report |date=1 March 2022 |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2022/2/28/us-announces-plan-to-expel-russian-diplomats-from-un-liveblog |newspaper=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] |access-date=23 March 2022 |archive-date=2022-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302193553/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2022/2/28/us-announces-plan-to-expel-russian-diplomats-from-un-liveblog }}</ref>后来有人在村子里发现了一个被俄罗斯军队杀害的平民的乱葬坑。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Piper |first1=Elizabeth |title=Dozens of Ukrainians Found in Grave near Kyiv as Battle Looms in East |url=https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-calls-more-sanctions-weapons-stop-russias-catastrophe-2022-04-10/ |access-date=April 10, 2022 |work=Reuters |date=April 10, 2022 |archive-date=2022-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220608060023/https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-calls-more-sanctions-weapons-stop-russias-catastrophe-2022-04-10/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Dozens of Civilians F